title: Ep63: It's Not You, It's Me Feat Wax Kyng

description:
We finally got Wax Kyng from the Brilliant Idiots in the damn studio and we dig into everything! We discuss a women's group urging Spotify to cancel artists with assault allegations, we bring back ice breaker questions with Wax, then we dig into dating. What happens when a woman comes on too strong and for men, when do you walk away from a "situation" before it gets too serious? Follow our guest on IG @waxkyng This show was sponsored by Talkspace.
